Introduction

Lee Daeyeol is a South Korean singer and dancer under Woollim Entertainment.

On March 31, 2017, Lee Daeyeol, along with Jae Seok and Dong Hyun, were introduced as part of the W PROJECT. He later debuted in the boy group Golden Child on August 28, 2017.

On December 27th, Woolim took to Weverse to announce that the exclusive contracts of Golden Child members Lee Daeyeol, Y, Bae Seungmin, Bong Jaehyun and Kim Donghyun will come to an end on December 31st.
